_sText:
This is a surf skill map.
There are 5 levels. The button at the start disables the jail system but can only be accessed by a admin that can noclip (good for people who want to just do the map). The levels get harder and harder but level 5 is the easiest as i forgot to make it level 2 but oh well, there is a time limit of 4 - 5 minutes. If you complete the map, you get a choice of which gun you want (awp, auto or scout) and everyone else get knifes. Enjoy the map?
